<HEADLINE>
<P>
'WAR AND REMEMBRANCE' TO CONCLUDE IN MAY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ABC said Wednesday that the final 11 1/2 hours of its mega-miniseries "War and 
Remembrance" will air over a five-night period starting Sunday, May 7. 
</P>
<P>
"Remembrance" is the $110-million sequel to ABC's 1983 blockbuster "The Winds 
of War." It proved a ratings misfire last November when its opening 18-hour 
installment aired. 
</P>
</TEXT>
