Toshio Sugasawa, Hoya Crystal artist, was spotlighted at a reception at 
Bullocks Wilshire to kick off the ARCS Foundation Scientist of the Year dinner. 
. . . 
</P>
<P>
Young patients from Orthopedic Hospital mixed with Pinafores of the League for 
Crippled Children at their annual Egg Roll at the Beverly Wilshire. Jann McCord 
was chairman. . . . 
</P>
