The English Speaking Union and the Shakespeare Globe Centre, Western Region, 
watched budding Shakespeareans compete in recitations at the Los Angeles 
Athletic Club, then honored them at dinner. 
</P>
<P>
FOR HARVARD: Mary Ann Shoptaw and Vicki Whitney co-chair the Harvard Roundup 
Sunday. Lots of Harvard parents are involved: Linda Adams, Suzi Given, Sally 
Field, Peter O'Malley, Joe Mandel, Carolyn Starkman, Dr. Mary Lou Ozohan. 
</P>
