<P>
NEWSWIRE: NAMES IN THE NEWS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Yankees' Ron Guidry, attempting to continue his pitching career at 38, has 
bone chips in his left elbow that may require surgery. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Column 
</P>
</TYPE>
