<P>
Wild Art 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA031689-0155 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 31643 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
March 16, 1989, Thursday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Long Beach; Part 9; Page 2; Column 2 
</P>
</SECTION>
