HEROIN-RELATED DEATHS,1973-'88 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Clipboard researched by Dallas Jamison and Rick VanderKnyff / Los Angeles 
Times. Graphics by Doris Shields / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
