<P>
Deal for Sports Gear Maker: Freeman Spogli &amp; Co., a Los Angeles private 
merchant banking firm, and an international investment group primarily from 
Austria have agreed to acquire the Sports Products Group of Minneapolis-based 
Minstar Inc. for $160 million in cash plus the assumption of about $100 million 
