POLICY; BUSH, GEORGE; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN AID -- NICARAGUA; GUERRILLAS -- 
NICARAGUA; HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES (U.S.); DEMOCRATIC PARTY 
</P>
